# 🛍️ React E-Commerce Store

This is a simple React-based e-commerce frontend using [DummyJSON API](https://dummyjson.com/). It features categories, product listings, product details, login, cart, and responsive design.

---

## 🚀 Features

- DummyJSON API Integration
- Category-wise browsing (Men, Women, Kids, Accessories, etc.)
- Product detail view
- Shopping cart (with global state)
- Responsive design using Tailwind CSS
- React Router for navigation

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- React
- React Router
- Tailwind CSS
- Context API
- Vite
- DummyJSON API

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ecommerce-react-app.git
cd ecommerce-react-app
npm install
npm run dev
